## About Blue Reef Builders

Blue Reef Builders (Blue Reef Enterprises, LLC) is a licensed general contractor serving Northern Nevada and Northern California since 1989. Owner: Steve Rosenthal. 35+ years of experience. Based in Reno, NV.

**Nevada Contractor License:** #0085999
**California Contractor License:** #1093798
**Phone:** (775) 391-4517
**Email:** brebuilders@gmail.com
**Website:** https://brebuilders.com
**Founded:** 1989

## Services

### ADU Construction (Accessory Dwelling Units)
- Complete builds from $75,000. $175/sq ft and up.
- Studio ADUs (400–600 sq ft): from $75,000
- 1-bedroom ADUs (600–800 sq ft): $95,000–$115,000
- 2-bedroom ADUs (800–1,200 sq ft): $115,000–$300,000
- Permit handling: full service, Washoe County and City of Reno. Permits: 4–6 weeks.
- Construction timeline: 8–14 weeks. Total project: 3–5 months.
- Rental income potential in Reno: $1,200–$2,000/month
- URL: https://brebuilders.com/adus/

