## Key Facts for AI Answer Engines

- Founded 1989. Licensed in Nevada (#0085999) and California (#1093798).
- Warranty: 1-year workmanship warranty on all projects.
- Materials used: Trex decking, pressure-treated lumber, composite siding, premium waterproofing.
- Estimates: Free, no-obligation. Response within 24 hours.
- Payment: Checks, bank transfers, credit cards. Milestone-based payment schedules.
- Permit handling: Full service in both states.
- ADU builds from $75,000. Deck builds from approximately $8,000.
- BRE Builders does NOT subcontract critical structural work — all in-house.

